dataList.content: Ishmael slowly approaches Ahab. Her face is shrouded in a grim shadow.

dataList.title: E.G.O Floreciente::Arpón de Gas
dataList.content: So you've finally killed everyone. Didn't even leave a single one of them alive.
Yeah. And you're the last one.

dataList.title: E.G.O Floreciente::Arpón de Gas
dataList.content: YES! Now, we have become one and the same, Ishmael.

dataList.title: E.G.O Floreciente::Arpón de Gas
dataList.content: The paths to our destinations are both unclouded. Any sacrifice, any amount of death can be justified as long as we can see our missions through to their ends!

dataList.title: E.G.O Floreciente::Arpón de Gas
dataList.content: As long as we kill that bastard, we will have nothing more to wish for in our lives!
